---
title: Chipotle Chicken Asado-Inspired Tacos with Charred Poblanos
description: For this dish, citrus-marinated chicken gets broiled with poblanos for a smoky-sweet bite. Salty feta and savoury, juicy tomatoes are the perfect toppers for this week's taco party.
